<<Discription of coral.option file>>

The key word is only one.

=========================
CsField From database
=========================
If you put these three words to option file,
Field data will be read from database.
If you comment out this line, field data is loaded from ascii file. 

Data type for three magnets
Solenoid : calculated value
SM1      : select with detector.dat
	   If flag2 is equal to 0, loaded calculated value.
	   IF flag2 is equal to 1, loaded measured value.
	   But pole distance is only 172cm for both.
SM2	 : select with detector.dat
	   current is current in SM2. 
	   
